These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, gardening, video-games, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, country, gospel
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the fan gospel##3
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is not the fan hip-hop##6
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking milk or the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan country, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking milk and the fan dubstep have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the fan country##3
 8. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5
 9. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | milk   | soy-milk      | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing     | video-games | gardening | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | country       | dubstep | gospel         | hip-hop     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, garlic, broccoli, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, canadian, german, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, goat, rat
 1. the chinese is the person eating pomegranate or the owner of the rat is the chinese, but not both##10
 2. the german is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 3. the chinese is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 4. the owner of the goat and the chinese have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
 9. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
10. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
11. the pakistani is in an even position##4
12. the chinese is the person eating grapefruit or the chinese is the owner of the rat, but not both##10
13. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person eating broccoli##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | pomegranate | garlic    | grapefruit | broccoli    |
| Nationality   | german   | chinese | canadian  | pakistani |
| Pet           | goat     | rat    | hamster    | chinchilla    |

