2. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
3. the person eating orange is the polish or the person eating orange is the person drinking cola, but not both##10
4. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
5. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
6. the malaysian is between the person eating apple and the british##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade         | juice     | cola | 7up |
| Food          | apple | pineapple | orange         | artichoke   |
| Nationality   | canadian     | malaysian   | british       | polish   |

