.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, lettuce, cherry, artichoke
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, card-games, dancing, board-games
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, turkish, russian, japanese
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the turkish##1
 2. the indonesian is not to the right of the person eating cherry##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the indonesian##6
 6. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the russian or the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating lettuce, but not both##10
 8. the russian is the person eating cherry or the russian is the person who's hobby is card-games, but not both##10
 9. the japanese is somewhere between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person eating cherry##7
10. the japanese is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | artichoke  | strawberry   | lettuce | cherry  |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing     | dancing  | card-games | board-games |
| Nationality   | indonesian | turkish | japanese  | russian |

