.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, almond-milk, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, satire, animation
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, chinchilla, hamster
 1. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the turtle is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
 3. the owner of the goat is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching epic movies##2
 4. the person drinking coffee is not the person watching animation movies##6
 5. the owner of the hamster and the person watching epic movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching epic movies or the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the turtle, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking tea##7
12. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | tea | coffee | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | martial-arts    | epic   | animation |
| Pet           | turtle    | goat | chinchilla    | hamster  |

