 4. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating onion and the owner of the rat##7
 5. the owner of the rat and the person eating pepper have the same parity positions##9
 6. the freelancer is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 7. the project-manager is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 8. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is the coach or the owner of the mouse is the person eating cucumber, but not both##10
10. the owner of the mouse and the freelancer have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3        |     4      |
